('19772', '3', 'Meanwhiile, drain oranges, reserving 2 Tbsp. of the liquid.'),
('19772', '4', 'Place reserved liquid in medium bowl.'),
('19772', '5', 'Add remaining 2 Tbsp. mustard, the oil, vinegar and ginger; beat with wire whisk until well blended.'),
('19772', '6', 'Cover large platter with spinach.'),
('19772', '7', 'Cut chicken diagonally into thin slices; arrange over spinach.  Top with oranges; drizzle with dressing.'),
